# Data directory

Place datasets under this directory before training.

Expected citation/coauthorship layout:

```text
data/
  cocitation/
    cora/
    citeseer/
  coauthorship/
    cora/
    dblp/
```

Each citation/coauthorship directory must contain `features.pickle`,
`labels.pickle`, and `hypergraph.pickle` from the HyperGCN-format data.

For `ModelNet40` and `NTU2012`, place the corresponding `.content` and `.edges`
files in `data/ModelNet40/` and `data/NTU2012/`.
